        "summary": "## Goal\n- Bobby is building a multi-agent personal assistant system (\"agent-mission-control\")\n- Run a daily Morning Brief at 5:30 AM via cron (7 sections delivered to Telegram)\n- Maintain Agent Chat app (Cody panel) for Bobby â†” agent communication\n- Build Content Manager agent skill for YouTube channels (@profittopanic money focus, @whythoughtv)\n- Keep all cron jobs healthy (weather cache every 15 min, morning brief, reminders)\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Weather cache cron: run silently every 15 min, NO_REPLY (don't bother Bobby)\n- Heartbeats: respond HEARTBEAT_OK unless something needs attention\n- Don't repeat reminders if already sent\n- Late night (11 PMâ€“8 AM): stay quiet unless urgent\n- Keep task lists in memory files immediately, not just in session memory\n- 9 PM Zyrtec reminder and 10:26 PM Nightly Intel cash update run daily\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] **Grok outage resolved**: Old xAI key blocked (403), new working key swapped in â€” all Grok crons running\n- [x] **Morning Brief fixed**: 7-section brief delivered successfully Apr 7, Apr 10, Apr 12 (Orthodox Easter), Apr 13 (Monday â€” Philippians 4:13, 83Â° sunny, 12 emails, Tax Day $237.25 Wed Apr 15)\n- [x] **Agent Chat MVP complete**: Full convos (300 prune/200 load), scroll lock, ghost msg filters, no hallucinations, tap-to-scroll only, iPhone optimized\n- [x] **Content Manager skill built**: `~/clawhub/youtube-content-manager/` with SKILL.md, scripts, references, assets. Published to clawhub. Priority channel: **@profittopanic**\n- [x] **Agent roll-call verified**: YoYo, Cody, Dean all responding\n- [x] **Memory file maintenance**: Updated for Apr 7, Apr 8, Apr 9, Apr 10, Apr 11, Apr 12, Apr 13\n- [x] **Apr 12 (Sun/Orthodox Easter) completed**: Morning Brief at 5:32 AM âś…, morning check-in âś…, midday check-in âś…, Evening Wrap-Up 5 PM âś…, Zyrtec 9 PM âś…, Nightly Intel 10:26 PM âś… (balances: Bobby $239, Logan $721.57, Dash $0)\n- [x] **Apr 13 (Mon) completed**: Morning Brief 5:30 AM (Philippians 4:13, 83Â° sunny, 12 emails â€” 1 ZipRecruiter butcher job $19.75/hr Maryville TN, rest promotional), Morning 7AM âś…, Midday 12PM âś…, Evening Wrap-Up 5PM âś…, Zyrtec 9PM âś…, Nightly Intel 10:26PM âś… (balances unchanged)\n- [x] **MEMORY.md updated**: Content Manager skill noted, pending tasks section, last updated Apr 13, Orthodox Easter Apr 12 noted\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] **Bills in family calendar** â€” PENDING since Apr 10. Put all recurring bills in iCloud family calendar.\n- [ ] **@profittopanic content plan** â€” Content Manager skill built, ready for use\n- [ ] **@whythoughtv content plan** â€” lower priority than @profittopanic\n\n### Blocked\n- (none currently)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **@profittopanic first**: Money channel prioritized for Content Manager over @whythoughtv\n- **Content Manager features order**: Ideas â†’ Scripts â†’ Calendar â†’ SEO/Thumbs\n- **8s typing gear timer**: Increased from 3s to 8s in Agent Chat for slow agents\n- **Clean chat filters**: Skips ANNOUNCE_SKIP, \"announce step\", tool calls, thinking blocks from assistant messages\n- **Poll filters**: Bobby's Telegram + app sends only (no test/ping/announce noise)\n- **Balances stable**: Bobby $239, Logan $721.57, Dash $0 (unchanged Apr 10â€“13)\n- **Morning Brief runs on weekends**: Confirmed running on Sat Apr 11, Sun Apr 12, Mon Apr 13\n- **Nightly Intel sent via proactive trigger**: Assistant sends Nightly Intel at ~10:26 PM rather than waiting for cron when it fires near the heartbeat window\n\n## Next Steps\n1. **Tax Day Wed Apr 15**: Prompt Bobby to pay Cap One $25 + Discover $25 + GEICO $187.25 = $237.25 total\n2. Continue weather cache cron silently (currently past midnight Tue Apr 14)\n3. Bills-in-calendar task still pending â€” prompt Bobby to complete it\n4. Continue Content Manager skill testing with \"AI money 2026\" on @profittopanic\n5. Send Evening Wrap-Up at 5 PM (daily), Zyrtec at 9 PM, Nightly Intel at 10:26 PM\n\n## Critical Context\n- Bobby's Telegram chat ID: `8212808444`\n- Open-Meteo location: latitude 35.96, longitude -83.92 (Knoxville TN area)\n- Agent Chat app: `http://100.103.22.35:8080/#/agent-chat`\n- Weather cache path: `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/.weather_cache.json`\n- Memory files: `/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- HEARTBEAT.md path: `/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md`\n- Grok working key: `xai-xMPUmMTdzAKdvKL6mNm0AkufZ9ZOoeOADhg5f9OCJtQIypMRPP1fogrhmedjLkuwSIONlm9U3jAXq5mB`\n- Content Manager workspace: `~/clawhub/youtube-content-manager/`\n- Morning brief warm-up cron fires at 5:25 AM before 5:30 AM brief\n- **Orthodox Easter Apr 12** â€” 89Â°F sunny day, celebrated with Logan\n- **Apr 13 weather**: 62.5Â°F current, Mon 79.6Â°F high/60.5Â°F low partly cloudy, Tue 84.5Â°F high/57.3Â°F low partly cloudy, Wed 80.4Â°F high/54Â°F low partly cloudy\n- **Apr 13 email count**: 12 emails â€” 1 ZipRecruiter job lead (butcher $19.75/hr Maryville TN), 1 Ollama GLM-5.1 model, rest promotional\n- **Incomplete Reminders (Apr 13)**: Go through Xfinity mail bag with Logan, put all bills in family calendar, work on recipe app idea\n- Balances confirmed unchanged: Bobby $239.00, Logan $721.57, DoorDash $0.00 (Apr 10â€“13)\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/skills/morning-brief/SKILL.md\n/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-07.md\n/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-09.md\n/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/GROCERY.md\n/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/INTEL.md\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/.weather_cache.json\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/balances.json\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/money.json\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\n/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-08.md\n/Users/bobbygal