ker, alex finn transcripts, OpenClaw Gateway.webloc\n\n### Blocked\n- ~~**Grok API down**: xAI returning 403~~ âś… RESOLVED â€” new working key\n- ~~**RecipeRip missing dotenv**~~ âś… RESOLVED\n- ~~**Cron failure alerts**~~ â€” partially resolved; silent mode eliminates \"sent and delivered\" but NOT \"âš ď¸Ź âŹ° Cron failed\" gateway alerts; those are system-level and cannot be disabled via config\n- ~~**Location-based \"when I get home\" reminders**~~ â€” NOT reliably achievable; cron cannot fetch specific Telegram message by ID; live location updates come through as new messages in chat\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **All crons on `mode: \"none\"`**: Bobby annoyed at \"âś… Reminder sent and delivered\" system spam; all crons (Zyrtec, Flonase, Nightly Intel, Check-Ins, Valvoline, Home Reminder) now silent\n- **Cron failure alerts NOT suppressible**: \"âš ď¸Ź âŹ° Cron failed\" gateway alerts fire at system level; `failureAlert` field removed but alerts still come through; MiniMax 529 overload errors at ~11 PM-midnight caused recent failures\n- **Check-in crons set up at Bobby's request**: 7 AM / 12 PM / 5 PM â€” full daily coverage; Bobby wants proactive management\n- **\"When I get home\" location detection**: NOT technically achievable without polling Telegram API or Bobby resending location; Bobby frustrated by my repeated \"send me your location\"; I committed to checking message 22073 without asking for resends\n- **Morning Brief reminders cleanup**: Bobby corrected â€” taxes done, Amazon done, SuperGrok not needed, job search not needed, Xfinity cancelled, Easter already celebrated\n- **Location always from message 22073**: Bobby's live location sent to me in Telegram thread; I should always go back to that message to get latest coordinates rather than asking him to resend\n- **Agent-to-agent via sessions_send**: Works; Rex replied directly to Bobby on Telegram; agents can text Bobby without Dean as relay\n- **Dreaming confirmed working but slow-building**: First dream diaries from April 11, 3 AM; poetic narrative format; processes 778 \"assistant\" + 639 \"user\" memories; not instantly actionable\n- **OpenClaw 2026.4.10 update**: Active Memory plugin most impactful for Bobby; Codex provider for agent code; MLX speech experimental; Seedance 2.0 video\n- **New DD goal: $164/day**: Bobby's updated DoorDash earnings target\n- **Patriot Bonds as backup**: Emergency financial resource if DD slows\n- **Breakfast for two**: Bobby to make eggs/toast/bacon/OJ for himself and Logan Sunday morning; 6 AM reminder (after Morning Brief)\n\n## Next Steps\n1. **Wait for xAI response** on grok-4.1 enablement (team `09c1d36c-fb69-4d0f-9c0c-f274269a8a39`); once enabled, switch crons from MiniMax to `xai/grok-4.1-fast-non-reasoning`\n2. **Tonight**: Logan rĂ©sumĂ© help reminder at 2 AM; Zyrtec at 9 PM; Nightly Intel at 10:26 PM\n3. **Tomorrow morning (April 12)**: Breakfast for Bobby + Logan at 6 AM (eggs, toast, bacon, OJ); Morning Brief at 5:30 AM\n4. **April 17**: Engine coolant + cabin air filter reminder at 5 PM\n5. **July 9**: Next oil change reminder (day before July 10, 2026 estimate)\n6. **April 15 (Tax Day)**: Cap One $25 + Discover $25 + GEICO $187.25 on Family Calendar â€” verify autopay working\n7. **Ongoing**: Monitor DD earnings vs $164/day goal; update moving calendar in Nightly Intel\n8. **Future**: Set up shared team log file for agent-to-agent info sharing (deferred from discussion); Shared memory file at `~/agent-mission-control/data/shared-memory.json` already exists\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Cron IDs**:\n  - MC Watchdog: `4a078218` â†’ MiniMax, every 5 min, mode: none âś…\n  - Morning Brief Warm-Up: `e63a926f` â†’ MiniMax âś…\n  - Morning Brief: `0c8b1d5b` â†’ MiniMax âś…\n  - Zyrtec Night: `ecc194aa` â†’ MiniMax, 9 PM daily âś…\n  - Flonase Morning: `295537b1` â†’ MiniMax, 9 AM daily âś…\n  - Nightly Intel: `b693b56a` â†’ MiniMax, 10:26 PM daily âś…\n  - Emmy Email Check: `d64702cd` â†’ MiniMax, hourly âś…\n  - Weather Cache Refresh: `720739ac` â†’ MiniMax, every 15 min âś…\n  - 7 AM Check-In: `6df3c7ab-d496-40e7-a556-e2b20ae9c4d1` âś…\n  - 12 PM Check-In: `061e3010-30d3-47a3-871e-9c8f3688960a` âś…\n  - 5 PM Wrap-Up: `1e722757-d789-4791-979c-40ace721311c` âś…\n  - Valvoline 9 AM: `72056828-4596-45a4-a40c-3975a1f4ed2a` â†’ deleteAfterRun âś…\n  - Home Reminder: `b5fd8c58-78dc-47b5-804c-fb033af2e3f0` â†’ deleted âś…\n  - Hockey Traffic 4:30 PM: `fc07f97b-5b36-458a-b1aa-2c69d1de6dc6` âś…\n  - Bills Calendar 1:30 PM: `c90f82df-171e-473f-b751-11354b9cc2ac` âś…\n  - Cabin Air + Coolant Check: `7ae305bb-3c41-407d-a340-a9c958b3aef2` â†’ April 17, 5 PM âś…\n  - Breakfast Tomorrow: `ae8f6a47-61fc-49b7-b614-7101407e3871` â†’ April 12, 6 AM âś…\n  - Logan Resume: `74848213-c740-441f-b216-e951b4344390` â†’ April 11, 2 AM âś…\n  - Next Oil Change: `23feb105-d412-4a3f-b94a-5ff8cb0abcc5` â†’ July 9, 2026 noon âś…\n  - Location Watch Test: `97d21697` â†’ DELETED (spam caused) âś…\n- **Gateway**: PID on loopback, Tailscale at `100.103.22.35`\n- **OpenClaw**: 2026.4.10 (updated April 10, 2026)\n- **Working xAI key**: `xai-xMPUmMTwzAKdvKL6mNm0AkufZ9ZOoeOADhg5f9OCJtQIypMRPP1fogrhmedjLkuwSIONlm9U3jAXq5mB`\n- **xAI team ID**: `09c1d36c-fb69-4d0f-9c0c-f274269a8a39`\n- **Bobby's location**: 1911 Mobley Way 37922 #202 (Knoxville, TN 37922)\n- **Hockey venue**: 500 Howard Baker Jr Ave, Knoxville, TN 37915 (Civic Coliseum); puck drop 6:15 PM; departed 5:15 PM\n- **Live location message**: Telegram message id 22073 â€” Bobby's live location thread; always reference this for location\n- **Bills due**:\n  - April 11: Affirm T-Mobile $25.74 (PAID âś…)\n  - April 12: Affirm T-Mobile $29.87\n  - April 15: Cap One $25, Discover $25, GEICO $187.25 (Tax Day)\n  - April 17: Affirm T-Mobile $15.31\n  - April 21: Affirm T-Mobile $18.00\n  - April 27: Affirm + Cap One Quicksilver $424.41\n- **Grocery list (Apple Reminders, Grocery)**: Mouthwash, Gum, Hotdogs, Hotdog buns (added April 10-11); Laundry sanitizer (pending)\n-