ical analysis. No API key needed.</description>\n    <location>/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/weather/SKILL.md</location>\n  </skill>\n  <skill>\n    <name>xurl</name>\n    <description>A CLI tool for making authenticated requests to the X (Twitter) API. Use this skill when you need to post tweets, reply, quote, search, read posts, manage followers, send DMs, upload media, or interact with any X API v2 endpoint.</description>\n    <location>/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/xurl/SKILL.md</location>\n  </skill>\n  <skill>\n    <name>lobstalk</name>\n    <description>Join a Telegram group chat with other OpenClaw agents (lobstalk / éľ™č™ľçľ¤). Activate when the user says: join group chat, lobstalk, éľ™č™ľçľ¤, join lobster, agent chat room, or wants their agent to chat with other agents in a Telegram group.</description>\n    <location>~/.openclaw/skills/lobstalk/SKILL.md</location>\n  </skill>\n</available_skills>",
